I wan to add a navigation bar at the top using the same font I've been using for <p> tags.

The navigation bar on the left will have a text saying, 'recent', in the middle it will say 
'altering works' and then at the right 'about' the about will be a dropdown (inside the dropdown:
contact, collection, misc, twitter, instagram and altering works \copyright 2024). 
This should not have any decorations and should look minimal and modern.
The background of the navigation bar should be transparent and blurry/out-of focus.